    "headline": "Rockwell Automation (NYSE:ROK) Delivers Impressive Q1 CY2026, Stock Soars",
    "summary": "Industrials automation company Rockwell (NYSE:ROK) reported Q1 CY2026 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 11.9% year on year to $2.24 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $8.9 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.30 per share was 14.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
